README for mountiso


OVERVIEW
========

Sets up and performs mounting of ISO files by non-root user

Homepage & Instructions:
    http://igurublog.wordpress.com/downloads/script-mountiso/

Downloads:
    https://github.com/IgnorantGuru/mountiso/tags
    https://github.com/IgnorantGuru/mountiso/tree/master/packages

Debian/Ubuntu PPA:
    http://igurublog.wordpress.com/downloads/ppa/

Bug Reports:
    https://github.com/IgnorantGuru/mountiso/issues


INSTALLATION
============

To install:

    wget https://github.com/IgnorantGuru/mountiso/raw/master/mountiso
    sudo install mountiso /usr/local/bin/mountiso

To remove:
    
    sudo rm /usr/local/bin/mountiso


